    <item>
      <title>Hardening Linux Servers</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/notes/hardening-linux-servers/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/notes/hardening-linux-servers/</guid>
      <description>
        
        
        &lt;h1&gt;1. Update &amp;amp;&amp;amp; Upgrade dos pacotes do sistema&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;Faça o update e upgrade dos pacotes de acordo com a distribuição de Linux.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;mt-4 flex w-max min-w-full border-b border-gray-200 pb-px dark:border-neutral-800&#34;&gt;&lt;button
      class=&#34;tabs-toggle data-[state=selected]:border-primary-500 data-[state=selected]:text-primary-600 mr-2 rounded-t p-2 font-medium leading-5 transition-colors -mb-0.5 select-none border-b-2 border-transparent text-gray-600 hover:border-gray-200 hover:text-black dark:text-gray-200 dark:hover:border-neutral-800 dark:hover:text-white&#34;
      role=&#34;tab&#34;
      type=&#34;button&#34;
      aria-controls=&#34;tabs-panel-0&#34;
      aria-selected=&#34;true&#34;
      tabindex=&#34;0&#34;
      data-state=&#34;selected&#34;
    &gt;Debian&lt;/button&gt;&lt;button
      class=&#34;tabs-toggle data-[state=selected]:border-primary-500 data-[state=selected]:text-primary-600 mr-2 rounded-t p-2 font-medium leading-5 transition-colors -mb-0.5 select-none border-b-2 border-transparent text-gray-600 hover:border-gray-200 hover:text-black dark:text-gray-200 dark:hover:border-neutral-800 dark:hover:text-white&#34;
      role=&#34;tab&#34;
      type=&#34;button&#34;
      aria-controls=&#34;tabs-panel-1&#34;
      
      
      
    &gt;Ubuntu&lt;/button&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;
  
    &lt;div
  class=&#34;tabs-panel rounded pt-6 hidden data-[state=selected]:block&#34;
  id=&#34;tabs-panel-0&#34;
  role=&#34;tabpanel&#34;
  tabindex=&#34;0&#34;
  data-state=&#34;selected&#34;
&gt;
  &lt;code&gt;apt update &amp;amp;&amp;amp; apt upgrade&lt;/code&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

    &lt;div
  class=&#34;tabs-panel rounded pt-6 hidden data-[state=selected]:block&#34;
  id=&#34;tabs-panel-1&#34;
  role=&#34;tabpanel&#34;
  
  
&gt;
  &lt;code&gt;apt update &amp;amp;&amp;amp; apt upgrade&lt;/code&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;


&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;h1&gt;2. Configurar o Hostname da máquina, com FQDN.&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;Configurar o &lt;em&gt;hostname&lt;/em&gt; do servidor pode facilitar a configuração de outros serviços.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;code-block relative mt-6 first:mt-0 group/code&#34;&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-shell&#34; data-lang=&#34;shell&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;hostnamectl set-hostname server1.example.com&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;opacity-0 transition group-hover/code:opacity-100 flex gap-1 absolute m-[11px] right-0 top-0&#34;&gt;
    &lt;button
      class=&#34;code-copy-btn group/copybtn transition-all active:opacity-50 bg-primary-700/5 border border-black/5 text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-900 rounded-md p-1.5 dark:bg-primary-300/10 dark:border-white/10 dark:text-gray-400 dark:hover:text-gray-50&#34;
      title=&#34;Copy code&#34;
    &gt;
      &lt;div class=&#34;group-[.copied]/copybtn:hidden copy-icon pointer-events-none h-4 w-4&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
      &lt;div class=&#34;hidden group-[.copied]/copybtn:block success-icon pointer-events-none h-4 w-4&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;/button&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;h1&gt;3. Criar um usuário diferente de root para o login&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;Crie um usuário que possua privelégios &lt;code&gt;root&lt;/code&gt; para que o login de &lt;code&gt;SSH&lt;/code&gt; seja feito principalmente por ele.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;code-block relative mt-6 first:mt-0 group/code&#34;&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-shell&#34; data-lang=&#34;shell&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;useradd -s /bin/bash -m user
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;usermod -aG root user&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;opacity-0 transition group-hover/code:opacity-100 flex gap-1 absolute m-[11px] right-0 top-0&#34;&gt;
    &lt;button
      class=&#34;code-copy-btn group/copybtn transition-all active:opacity-50 bg-primary-700/5 border border-black/5 text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-900 rounded-md p-1.5 dark:bg-primary-300/10 dark:border-white/10 dark:text-gray-400 dark:hover:text-gray-50&#34;
      title=&#34;Copy code&#34;
    &gt;
      &lt;div class=&#34;group-[.copied]/copybtn:hidden copy-icon pointer-events-none h-4 w-4&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
      &lt;div class=&#34;hidden group-[.copied]/copybtn:block success-icon pointer-events-none h-4 w-4&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;/button&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;h1&gt;4. SSH Security&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;Podemos tomar algumas medidas de segurança para proteger as conexões de SSH&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Remover acesso através de senha para o usuário &lt;code&gt;root&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mudar porta de acesso &lt;code&gt;default=22&lt;/code&gt; do SSH&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;h1&gt;4. Firewall&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;As portas básicas que precisamos para manter um servidor &lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Web&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt; (assumindo http e https).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;22 (SSH)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;80/tcp&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;443/tcp&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;8000/tcp (Coolify)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;h1&gt;Referências&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://docs.rackspace.com/docs/linux-hostname-change&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Linux Hostname Change&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.redhat.com/sysadmin/configure-hostname-linux&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Configure Hostname Linux&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.ionos.com/help/server-cloud-infrastructure/getting-started/important-security-information-for-your-server/deactivating-the-ssh-root-login/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Deactivating the SSH root login&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.cyberciti.biz/faq/how-to-disable-ssh-password-login-on-linux/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;How to disable ssh password login on Linux&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

      </description>
    </item>
    
